This directory should contain the following items:

- elife-58430-supp1-v2.xlsx file
  contains schizophrenia EWAS hits
  obtained from:  https://elifesciences.org/articles/58430
  located under:  Figures and data > Additional files > Supplementary Tables 1-14.
  exact address:  https://cdn.elifesciences.org/articles/58430/elife-58430-supp1-v2.xlsx

- 41366_2018_BFijo2017269_MOESM66_ESM.xlsx file
  contains BMI EWAS hits
  obtained from:  https://www.nature.com/articles/ijo2017269
  located under:  Supplementary information > Supplementary Tables (XLSX 296 kb)
  exact address:  https://static-content.springer.com/esm/art%3A10.1038%2Fijo.2017.269/MediaObjects/41366_2018_BFijo2017269_MOESM66_ESM.xlsx

- pone.0063812.s005.xls file
  contains smoking EWAS hits
  obtained from:  https://journals.plos.org/plosone/article?id=10.1371/journal.pone.0063812
  located under:  Supplementary information > Table S1
  exact address:  https://doi.org/10.1371/journal.pone.0063812.s005

- ewas_alz.csv file
  contains neuritic amyloid plaque burder EWAS hits
  obtained from:  https://pmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/articles/PMC4292795/
  located under:  Supplementary material > NIHMS614693-supplement-supp_tables_and_figs.doc > Supplementary Table 2 > manually extracted into csv file
  exact address:  data/EWAS/ewas_alz.csv
